{{Infobox XC3 Enemy |category = Unique Monster |name = Conqueror Deepwan |image = XC3 Conqueror Deepwan.png |caption = Conqueror Deepwan |type = [[Igna]] |level = 102 |area = [[Erythia Sea]] ([[Demihuman Gutter]]) |spawntime = Anytime |respawn = Yes |movement = Ground |detection = |exp = 4,611 |cp = 346 |sp = 5 |gold = 5,544 |hp = 5,630,400 |strength = 2,052 |healing = 737 |dexterity = 379 |agility = 355 |physdef = 25% |ethdef = 10% |critrate = 15% |guardrate-front = 20% |guardrate-side = 0% |guardrate-back = 0% }} '''Conqueror Deepwan''' is a [[Unique Monster (XC3)|Unique Monster]] in {{XC3}}. It is a member of the [[Igna]] family, and can be found at level 102 in the [[Demihuman Gutter]] in [[Erythia Sea]]. It forms the duo "The King-Kings" with [[King Krawkin]]. The [[King's Bash]] [[Battle Arts (XC3)|Art]] can be earned by the [[Soulhacker]] [[Class (XC3)|class]] for defeating it.
